| H-new-2     | Partially | Closed    | **Partial** ƒ?" replay path correct, but A13.1 still mentions removed flag. |
| H-new-3     | Partially | Closed    | **Partial** ƒ?" single-`SessionRecorder` enforced, but mixed `SessionRecorder` + `WorldHistoryRecorder({ captureCommandPayloads: true })` still has chain ambiguity. |
| H-new-4     | Yes       | Closed    | **Closed** |
| H-new-5     | Yes       | Closed    | **Closed** |
