- `executions` ƒ+? `result.history.executions`.
- `failures` ƒ+? `result.history.failures`.
- `snapshots` ƒ+? `[{ tick: result.tick, snapshot: result.snapshot }]`. Single entry; selfCheck will check the segment from `initialSnapshot` to this final snapshot. Future enhancement could add periodic snapshots via a scenario option.
- `markers` ƒ+? one assertion marker per `result.checks` outcome:
  ```
  { id, tick: result.tick, kind: 'assertion', provenance: 'engine',
    text: outcome.name, data: { passed: outcome.passed, failure: outcome.failure } }
  ```
